      <details class="faq-item" open>
        <summary>What if we need something between Sprint and Studio?</summary>
        <p>Tell us the scope. If it doesn&rsquo;t fit a tier, we&rsquo;ll quote a flat fee within 24 hours. We don&rsquo;t do hourly billing.</p>
      </details>
      <details class="faq-item">
        <summary>Do you sign NDAs?</summary>
        <p>Yes. Send yours at the start of the engagement and we&rsquo;ll counter-sign the same day.</p>
      </details>
      <details class="faq-item">
        <summary>Can you work with our existing brand?</summary>
        <p>Of course. About a third of our work is layered on top of an existing identity. We&rsquo;ll respect what&rsquo;s working and only push on what isn&rsquo;t.</p>
      </details>
      <details class="faq-item">
        <summary>What happens after launch?</summary>
        <p>Studio includes two weeks of post-launch support. After that, most clients move into a Partner engagement. You&rsquo;re never locked in.</p>
      </details>
      <details class="faq-item">
        <summary>How do we get started?</summary>
        <p>Email <a href="mailto:hello@designshifu.com">hello@designshifu.com</a> with the metric you&rsquo;re trying to move and the deadline. We&rsquo;ll reply with a yes, a no, or a referral the same day.</p>
      </details>
